title: Ultimates Ultimate Collection (Trade Paperback)
description:
Spider-Man and the Green Goblin. The X-Men and Magneto. Strange beings with incredible powers have risen up to
challenge the old order, and ordinary citizens are scared witless. The government’s solution: a small but lethal army known
as the Ultimates, created to protect us all from the newly rising threats to mankind! Millar and Hitch’s widescreen super hero epic helped define Marvel’s then-new Ultimate line of comics, now you can own all the action across two titanic trade
paperbacks! Collecting ULTIMATES #1-13.
Parental Advisory …$34.99
ISBN: 978-0-7851-4387-1
